{"word":"H4940 - מִשְׁפָּחָה - mishpâchâh - mish-paw-khaw' - Family","slug":"H4940","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מִשְׁפָּחָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mishpâchâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mish-paw-khaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Family"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05D7;&#x05D4; - mishpa&#x0302;cha&#x0302;h</b> - <i>mish-paw-khaw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H8192\">H8192</a> (compare <a href=\"#/H8198\">H8198</a>); a <i>family</i>, that is, circle of relatives; figuratively a <i>class</i> (of persons), a <i>species</i> (of animals) or <i>sort</i> (of things); by extension a <i>tribe</i> or <i>people: - </i>family, kind (-red)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8198\">H8198</a>"}]}